# 📁 server/.dockerignore - Backend Docker ignore file
# 🎯 Core function: Exclude unnecessary files from Docker build context
# 🔗 Key dependencies: Docker build optimization
# 💡 Usage: Reduce build context size and improve build speed

# Dependencies
node_modules
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Build outputs
dist
build

